            "Element": "Pulse",
            "Name": "Smiting Tempest",
            "Desc": "Transforms into the <@ba.key>Empyrean of Truth</> that grants these enhancements:\nZhuang Fangyi's basic attacks are enhanced and her actions are harder to interrupt;\nBattle skill <@ba.key>Mantra of Sundering</> gains a higher DMG multiplier and an increased effect range, and the final Thunder Strike also applies <#ba.pulseinflict>Electric Infliction</> to the target hit.\nCombo skill <@ba.key>Breath of Transformation</> gains a higher DMG multiplier, cooldown becomes {combo_cd_rate:0} times faster, and effects are applied to enemies within a small area.\nThe first casting of the battle skill <@ba.key>Mantra of Sundering</> on an available target does not consume SP nor <#ba.conduct>Electrification</>, and is guaranteed to create 3 <@ba.key>Sunderblades</> even if the target has no <#ba.conduct>Electrification</>.",
