        "108": {
            "Icon": "skillicon/icon_combo_skill_zhuangfy_01",
            "Element": "Pulse",
            "Name": "Breath of Transformation",
            "Desc": "COMBO TRIGGER: When the controlled operator's <#ba.lastcombo>Final Strike</> or Finisher hits an enemy with <#ba.pulseinflict>Electric Infliction</>.\nZhuang Fangyi creates a Xiranblitz Array that attacks the enemy and deals <@ba.pulse>Electric DMG</>. If the Array hits an enemy that has <#ba.pulseinflict>Electric Infliction</> stack(s), then it will <#ba.consume>consume</> the said <#ba.pulseinflict>Electric Infliction</> stack(s), forcibly apply <#ba.conduct>Electrification</>, and give Ultimate Energy based on the number of stacks <#ba.consume>consumed</>.\nIf <#ba.conduct>Electrification</> is forcibly applied to an enemy that already has <#ba.conduct>Electrification</>, then apply <#ba.statuslevel>Status Level</> +1 to the enemy's <#ba.conduct>Electrification</>.",
